[SN]TITLE[SN]
Christopher Tolofua: Saracens agree to sign France and Toulouse hooker

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Premiership and European Champions Cup holders Saracens have agreed a deal to sign France international Christopher Tolofua next summer.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 22-year-old hooker will join Sarries from Toulouse at the end of the 2016-17 French Top 14 season.
Tolofua, who has won four caps for France, has agreed a two-year contract at Allianz Park.
"I'm excited to play in England next season and test myself in the Premiership," he said.
